          "id": 1,
          "question": "<p><a name=\"1403\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><pre class=\"prettyprint lang-c_cpp\">double foo(int n)\n{\n    int i;\n    double sum;\n    if(n == 0)\n    {\n        return 1.0;\n    }\n    else\n    {\n        sum = 0.0;\n        for(i = 0; i &lt; n; i++)\n        {\n            sum += foo(i);\n        }\n        return sum;\n    }\n}\n</pre>\n\n<p>The space complexity of the above code is?</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>GATE CSE 2005 | Question: 81a</b></p>",
          "type": "single",
          "options": [
